# Testing

## Current state
- **No automated tests** (score 1/10)
- Critical logic: `computeSettlement`, `computeSplit`, `fmt`, `mergeLocalStorage`

## Regression checklist (manual, every change)
- [ ] Desktop Chrome
- [ ] Mobile viewport / WhatsApp in-app browser
- [ ] Home tab: total, paid cards, settlement
- [ ] Bills tab: history, fair share, download CSV
- [ ] Share tab: WhatsApp copy tone + amounts
- [ ] Care tab: chatbot chips, optional OCR
- [ ] Add bill → immediate local render → cloud save toast
- [ ] Offline / no token → localStorage pending
- [ ] Empty bills state
- [ ] Slow network (loading/skeleton behavior)
- [ ] Version banner when `version.json` stale

## Priority test targets (when adding tests)
1. `computeSettlement(total)` — Kalyan→Deepa/Venky, no Venky→Deepa
2. Fair share = total/3
3. `mergeLocalStorage` deduplication
4. `fmt` INR formatting

## New tests require approval for
- New test framework / npm dependencies
- Extracting JS to separate modules (architecture change)

## Self-review scores
Correctness, Performance, Readability, Security, Accessibility, Maintainability — each /10. Below 8 → explain why.
